# La Queta — always apply

- Product/repo name: **La Queta** (`la-queta`). Language taught: Catalan.
- Follow `STYLE_GUIDE.md`, `PRODUCT.md`, and `TECHNICAL_PLAN.md`.
- `prototype/` is frozen — read for reference only; never edit.
- Implement by phase: failing tests → structure → behaviour → green tests → update docs/rules if conventions changed.
- Stack: Flask + SQLAlchemy 2 + Alembic + SQLite + vanilla HTML/CSS/JS. No SPA frameworks or CSS frameworks unless plans change.
- Levels in scope: A1 and A2 only.
- Do not run linters unless the user asks.
- Prefer small, phase-scoped diffs; no unrelated refactors.
- Local app: `make run` (port 5001); also `make test` / `make seed` / `make upgrade`.
